      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/french-economy-shrinks-as-political-mayhem-erodes-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府垮台严重打击了企业和消费者的信心，欧洲两大经济体去年年底出现萎缩。]]></description>
